name: Lilith
description: There were men, wasn't even aware of what they were doing. They were tempted by the scent and view of this wonderful being, named ''Lilith'' and wanted to be with her in their delusional dreams. There were no dreams, of course, just lots of blood on the floor , spilled from the fight they've started to earn her love. Well, they actually won her love. Her love was ''hate'' after all...
